Version controlled dotfiles directory.
Perhaps I can get this working cross-platform and as minimalistic as possible.

To install:
Clone this repository from Github:
*** For example:
    git clone https://github.com/Happy-Dude/dotfiles.git ~/dotfiles

Vim configurations:
    * Make symbolic links to the vim configuration files (vimrc and gvimrc)
    *** For example:
        ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
        ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
    * Make symbolic link to vim directory
    *** For example:
        ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim ~/.vim

Tmux configurations:
    * Make symbolic link to tmux configuration
    *** For example:
        ln -s ~/dotfiles/tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf

